00F8BCB4.Line3.EEB24.Dru: Ah, guard yourself against the local gossip then.

832AA920.Line5.BAE4.Dru: I could not say. I am not from these parts.

F63F5232.Line1.EEB24.Dru: Why is it your kin loathe us, druid? We've done so much to heal this broken land, and still the glenfolk criticize our beliefs at every opportunity.
